Book:
    - Title
    - Cover
    - Description
    - Chapters
    - Characters
    - Worldbuilding properties (custom)
        - WorldbuildingCategory
        - WorldbuildingDetail
    - Genres

Character:
    - First Name
    - Middle name (optional)
    - Last name
    - Age
    - Physical description
        - Eye color
        - Hair color
        - Skin color
        - Weight
        - Height
    - Good traits
    - Bad traits
    - Main fear
    - Main wish

Chapter:
    - Title
    - Content
    - Book ID

Genre: 
    - Title

WorldbuildingProperty:
    - WorldBuildingCategory ID
    - WorldBuildingDetail ID

WorldbuildingCategory:
    - Title

WorldbuildingDetail:
    -Content
    -WorldbuildingCategory ID